{"tid":2187492,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超官方正式宣佈與中國轉播合作商PPTV解約","createTime":"2020-09-03T15:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:51:28.000Z","uid":34468,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd939ecfee92840ad7f9bb2f34fd85c810bd7c2","tid":2187492,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"【#體嘢突發】<br />\n<br />\n英超官方正式宣佈，英超正式與中國轉播合作商PPTV解約。PPTV聲明，已經按合約超額預付版權週期費用。<br />\n<br />\nPPTV以5.23億英鎊獲得了2019-2022三季英超在中國的獨家轉播版權，但根據《泰晤士報》記者Martyn Ziegler消息，英超將考慮終止與中國轉播商PPTV的合約，雙方曾簽下了一份為期三年的協議，然而<span class=\"red\">PPTV拖欠了首年1.6億英鎊的版權費已有半年。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據《Daily Mail》的最新講法，因為武漢肺炎疫情，PPTV本應在3月支付的版權費用被擱置，而按合約規定PPTV應當在2020年3月支付全部三年版權期80%的費用，於是引發了雙方分歧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/493520410798584/posts/1697188067098473/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F493520410798584%2Fposts%2F1697188067098473%2F&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=9387d1b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/493520410798584/posts/1697188067098473/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/54014827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F54014827&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=f978f75a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/54014827</a>"},{"pid":"fe8c294923324c4f726f0787f6346e78550ecee9","tid":2187492,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}